ook/">And we have a clip from Season 2 of <em>Poker Face</em>!</a></strong><span class="post_attribute center"><span class="post_detail_date">April 2, 2025</span> by <a href="https://crimereads.com/author/oliviarutigliano/">Olivia Rutigliano</a></span></div></li><li><div class="post_circle_thumb"><a href="https://crimereads.com/a-forensic-anthropologists-search-for-the-lost-boys-of-houston/"><img class="lazy" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/plugins/lb-content-widgets/img/lazy-sq.png" data-src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2025/04/prison-150x150.jpg" alt=""></a></div><div class="text-container"><strong class="title"><a href="https://crimereads.com/a-forensic-anthropologists-search-for-the-lost-boys-of-houston/">A Forensic Anthropologist's Search for the Lost Boys of Houston</a></strong><span class="post_attribute center"><span class="post_detail_date">April 2, 2025</span> by <a href="https://crimereads.com/author/liseolsen/">Lise Olsen</a></span></div></li><li><div class="post_circle_thumb"><a href="https://crimereads.com/bryan-gruley-on-research-inspiration-and-a-notorious-hockey-fight/"><img class="lazy" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/plugins/lb-content-widgets/img/lazy-sq.png" data-src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2025/03/hockey1-150x150.jpg" alt=""></a></div><div class="text-container"><strong class="title"><a href="https://crimereads.com/bryan-gruley-on-research-inspiration-and-a-notorious-hockey-fight/">Bryan Gruley on Research, Inspiration, and a Notorious Hockey Fight</a></strong><span class="post_attribute center"><span class="post_detail_date">April 2, 2025</span> by <a href="https://crimereads.com/author/briangruley/">Bryan Gruley</a></span></div></li></ul></li>
